37:22.640 --> 37:25.920
I'm so sorry. We... We don't
know what's wrong with her.

37:26.080 --> 37:29.280
It's okay. I just heard
the front door.

37:30.280 --> 37:31.960
Where is Em?

37:34.000 --> 37:35.440
Shepherd my guiding spirits

37:35.600 --> 37:38.320
and bind me to the person
in my thoughts.

37:45.560 --> 37:47.600
Rebecca.

37:47.760 --> 37:49.680
Honey.

37:52.280 --> 37:54.800
<i>I can't help you.</i>

37:54.960 --> 37:57.640
No.

37:57.800 --> 38:00.280
It's Diana who needs help.

38:00.440 --> 38:02.560
We're trying to understand the book.

38:02.720 --> 38:05.120
She's connected to it somehow.

38:05.280 --> 38:07.600
<i>Understand this.</i>

38:07.760 --> 38:11.120
<i>There will be dark times</i>
<i>and great losses.</i>

38:11.280 --> 38:14.120
<i>But the book will change everything.</i>

38:14.280 --> 38:17.200
-Rebecca.
<i>-Once it's completed,</i>

38:17.360 --> 38:20.480
<i>the book is going to reveal itself.</i>

38:20.640 --> 38:24.720
But we only have this page.
How do we complete it?

38:24.880 --> 38:27.320
Where are the other pages?

38:27.480 --> 38:31.080
<i>You're in danger.</i>
<i>He wants the page.</i>

38:37.240 --> 38:40.440
-Bring it back.
-Never.

38:40.600 --> 38:43.760
Give me... the page.

38:43.920 --> 38:45.920
Go to hell!

38:50.560 --> 38:55.440
You are so consumed
with power and greed.

38:55.600 --> 38:58.400
You lost your soul to the darkness.

38:58.560 --> 39:02.040
Surrender the page.

39:05.520 --> 39:07.040
I've searched the house.
She's not here.

39:07.200 --> 39:10.280
She's taken what she needs.
I know where she's gone.

39:13.560 --> 39:16.080
Can you sense her?

39:16.240 --> 39:19.240
There's someone else close by.

39:20.320 --> 39:21.720
A powerful creature.

39:21.880 --> 39:24.000
Protect the baby.

39:25.760 --> 39:28.480
I am not afraid of you, Peter.

39:28.640 --> 39:33.440
I will always fight for Diana.
She will always come first.

39:33.600 --> 39:37.280
-She abandoned you.
-She will be back!

39:37.440 --> 39:41.120
She will be more powerful
than you can imagine.

39:41.280 --> 39:42.640
The page!

39:42.800 --> 39:45.880
Diana will unite all creatures

39:46.040 --> 39:47.840
against bigots like you.

39:56.400 --> 39:59.680
And she will avenge me!

40:31.480 --> 40:33.280
You threatened my friends.

40:33.440 --> 40:37.800
And now you dare to come here,
to my territory.

40:37.960 --> 40:40.800
The witches belong to me.

40:48.360 --> 40:52.480
Young bucks should never
break from the herd.

40:53.960 --> 40:58.920
Now, you pay the price.

40:59.080 --> 41:02.840
This is de Clermont land.

41:03.000 --> 41:05.640
Em! Em!

41:05.800 --> 41:08.040
Kill me here...

41:08.200 --> 41:12.080
and you'll start a war
that you have no hope winning.

41:14.920 --> 41:16.880
You wouldn't dare!

41:18.320 --> 41:19.840
Sleep now.

41:21.000 --> 41:22.840
Em!

41:25.800 --> 41:28.120
Em!

41:28.280 --> 41:30.800
Em, wake up.

41:30.960 --> 41:33.360
Wake up, please!

41:33.520 --> 41:35.680
Em, wake up.

41:38.720 --> 41:42.680
Thank you for sharing this world
with me.

41:42.840 --> 41:45.880
I'm glad I got
to know Matthew Roydon.

41:48.320 --> 41:51.160
I've had so many roles in my life.

41:52.520 --> 41:57.200
But to be a husband
and a father again...

41:58.880 --> 42:00.520
that's all I've ever wanted.

42:02.320 --> 42:04.760
Endings and beginnings.

42:18.480 --> 42:21.400
Let's go meet our future.

42:41.920 --> 42:44.800
Come on. Come on, Em.

42:44.960 --> 42:47.920
Please. Please.

42:48.080 --> 42:50.520
Come on, darling.
